<complexType name="contact_Type">
<annotation>
<documentation>
Contact information - roles are codeLists and should be restricted to file 'contactRoleCode.xml'. Eg.
<![CDATA[
<contact>
<name>...</name>
<telephonePrimary></telephonePrimary>
<telephoneSecondary></telephoneSecondary>
<fax>...</fax>
<e-mail>...</e-mail>
<role codeList="../../codeLists/contacts-roles-codelists.xml#Role-Contact" codeListValue="Primary">Primary Contact</role>
</contact>
]]>
</documentation>
</annotation>
<sequence>
<element name="name" type="string"/>
<element name="telephonePrimary" nillable="true" type="geo:telephoneOrFax_Type"/>
<element name="telephoneSecondary" nillable="true" type="geo:telephoneOrFax_Type"/>
<element name="fax" nillable="true" type="geo:telephoneOrFax_Type"/>
<element name="e-mail" type="string"/>
<element name="role" type="gmd:CI_RoleCode_PropertyType"/>
</sequence>
</complexType>
<complexType name="agencyPropertyType">
<annotation>
<documentation>
The agency contacts are of various types such as SiteOwner or SiteContact or ... , each with different possible occurences (0 or 1, 0 or more, 1 or more, 1 is required,...).
They have a security constraint to specify who can view the data (if confidential then the business rules decide on who can view the information).
And as per the gmd:CI_ResponsibleParty definition, the individuals indicated have a role specified in gmd:CI_RoleCode.
Eg.
<![CDATA[
<SiteOwner or SiteContact or SiteMetadataCustodian or SiteDataCenters or SiteDataSource gml:id="xyz">
<gmd:MD_SecurityConstraints>
<gmd:classification>
<gmd:MD_ClassificationCode codeList="http://xml.gov.au/icsm/geodesyml/codelists/agency-roles-codelists.xml#Security" codeListValue="Confidential">Confidential</gmd:MD_ClassificationCode>
</gmd:classification>
</gmd:MD_SecurityConstraints>
<gmd:CI_ResponsibleParty>
<gmd:individualName>
<gco:CharacterString>Ryan Ruddick</gco:CharacterString>
</gmd:individualName>
<gmd:organisationName>
<gco:CharacterString>Geoscience Australia</gco:CharacterString>
</gmd:organisationName>
...
<gmd:role>
<gmd:CI_RoleCode codeList="http://www.isotc211.org/2005/resources/Codelist/gmxCodelists.xml" codeListValue="pointOfContact">pointOfContact</gmd:CI_RoleCode>
</gmd:role>
</agency>
]]>
</documentation>
</annotation>
<complexContent>

<element ref="gmd:CI_ResponsibleParty"/>
</sequence>
<attributeGroup ref="gml:AssociationAttributeGroup"/>
</extension>
</complexContent>
</complexType>
